<subSubSection id="FADC655816612E2EFF70FF041122FDB7" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="B27936D316612E2EFF70FF041122FDB7" blockId="2.[136,779,182,585]" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">
<emphasis id="80B2EAC116612E2EFF70FF041114FF37" bold="true" box="[136,266,182,201]" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="75C64D5016612E2EFED9FF04119DFF37" authorityName="Triques" authorityYear="1996" box="[289,387,182,201]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rhamphichthyidae" genus="Iracema" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="80B2EAC116612E2EFED9FF04119DFF37" box="[289,387,182,201]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">Iracema</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is distinguished from other rhamphichthyids by the following characteristics: 240-257 analfin rays (
<emphasis id="80B2EAC116612E2EFF1DFF4410E5FEF7" box="[229,251,246,265]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">vs</emphasis>
. 
<quantity id="753E9B3616612E2EFEFFFF441167FEF7" box="[263,377,246,265]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.445" metricValueMax="5.3594" metricValueMin="3.5305999999999997" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" unit="in" value="175.0" valueMax="211.0" valueMin="139.0">139-211 in</quantity>
<taxonomicName id="75C64D5016612E2EFE86FF441279FEF7" authorityName="Ellis. Triques" authorityYear="1996" box="[382,615,246,265]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rhamphichthyidae" genus="Gymnorhamphichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="80B2EAC116612E2EFE86FF441279FEF7" box="[382,615,246,265]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">Gymnorhamphichthys</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<quantity id="753E9B3616612E2EFD61FF441315FEF7" box="[665,779,246,265]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.8298" metricValueMax="11.937999999999999" metricValueMin="7.7216" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" unit="in" value="387.0" valueMax="470.0" valueMin="304.0">304-470 in</quantity>
<taxonomicName id="75C64D5016612E2EFF70FEA4112EFED7" box="[136,304,278,297]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rhamphichthyidae" genus="Rhamphichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="80B2EAC116612E2EFF70FEA4112EFED7" box="[136,304,278,297]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">Rhamphichthys</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); 15 or 16 pectoral-fin rays (
<emphasis id="80B2EAC116612E2EFD7BFEA41284FED7" box="[643,666,278,297]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">vs</emphasis>
. 
<quantity id="753E9B3616612E2EFD53FEA41314FED7" box="[683,778,278,297]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.921" metricValueMax="3.302" metricValueMin="2.54" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" unit="in" value="11.5" valueMax="13.0" valueMin="10.0">10-13 in</quantity>
<taxonomicName id="75C64D5016612E2EFF70FE84116FFEB7" authorityName="Ellis. Triques" authorityYear="1996" box="[136,369,310,329]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rhamphichthyidae" genus="Gymnorhamphichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="80B2EAC116612E2EFF70FE84116FFEB7" box="[136,369,310,329]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">Gymnorhamphichthys</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<quantity id="753E9B3616612E2EFE5CFE8411E3FEB7" box="[420,509,310,329]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.953" metricValueMax="5.588" metricValueMin="4.318" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" unit="in" value="19.5" valueMax="22.0" valueMin="17.0">17-22 in</quantity>
<taxonomicName id="75C64D5016612E2EFDFBFE8412B8FEB7" box="[515,678,310,329]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rhamphichthyidae" genus="Rhamphichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="80B2EAC116612E2EFDFBFE8412B8FEB7" box="[515,678,310,329]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">Rhamphichthys</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); a series of dark, rounded pigment blotches on the side of the body along the lateral line (
<emphasis id="80B2EAC116612E2EFE29FEC411F7FE77" box="[465,489,374,393]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">vs</emphasis>
. no pigmentation in 
<taxonomicName id="75C64D5016612E2EFF70FE24116FFE57" authorityName="Ellis. Triques" authorityYear="1996" box="[136,369,406,425]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rhamphichthyidae" genus="Gymnorhamphichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="80B2EAC116612E2EFF70FE24116FFE57" box="[136,369,406,425]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">Gymnorhamphichthys</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and dark oblique transverse bands or no pigmentation in 
<taxonomicName id="75C64D5016612E2EFEABFE0411E8FE37" box="[339,502,438,457]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rhamphichthyidae" genus="Rhamphichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="80B2EAC116612E2EFEABFE0411E8FE37" box="[339,502,438,457]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">Rhamphichthys</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); caudal filament ovoid in cross section, its depth slightly greater than its width (
<emphasis id="80B2EAC116612E2EFD5EFE6412A5FE17" box="[678,699,470,489]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">vs</emphasis>
. caudal filament laterally compressed in cross section, its depth about three times its width in 
<taxonomicName id="75C64D5016612E2EFE33FDA412CEFDD7" authorityName="Ellis. Triques" authorityYear="1996" box="[459,720,534,553]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rhamphichthyidae" genus="Gymnorhamphichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="80B2EAC116612E2EFE33FDA412CEFDD7" box="[459,720,534,553]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">Gymnorhamphichthys</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="75C64D5016612E2EFF70FD841132FDB7" box="[136,300,566,585]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rhamphichthyidae" genus="Rhamphichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="80B2EAC116612E2EFF70FD841132FDB7" box="[136,300,566,585]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">Rhamphichthys</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
